summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Mount Baker Boulevard from Thirtieth Avenue South to Thirty-third Avenue South et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 18800, creating Local Improvement District No. 1807 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
